{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_15121.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":100851,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm24_story07","chara":[{"id":303001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":100851,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"Please, say whatever you like."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"Ah! I'm sorry..."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"Umm... You want me to talk about myself?"},{"chara":[{"id":100851,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"Sure."},{"chara":[{"id":303001,"motion":301}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"Um, well..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":100851}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":303001,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"I work part-time at a flower shop called Blossom!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303001}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"Once, when the owner got sick,"},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"I was told the store was going to close..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_022.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"I wanted to help her get better@and protect Blossom..."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"So I became a Magical Girl to cure her illness."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"That wish came true, and I was able@to successfully save the shop, but..."},{"chara":[{"id":303001,"motion":301}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"In the not-to-distant future, when Auntie retires,@Blossom will cease to exist."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"Even if Auntie never got sick, it would've@happened in any number of ways."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"I was shaken...but then I realized,"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_022.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"I wasn't trying to protect Auntie or Blossom."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"I just didn't want to lose my happy \"present\"."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":301}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"I remembered those dark feelings I had@when I saw that Witch's portrait."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"It hurt so much..."},{"chara":[{"id":303001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"..."},{"bgmFadeOut":3000,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Konomi","textCenter":"But you know what, I'm back on my@feet now and looking forward!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":303001,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":100851,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"You found a solution?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"Well, in a way, yes?"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story19","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"I've been thinking about why@I insist on helping out at Blossom."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"When I was little, I was so happy@to receive flowers from Auntie."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"So I wanted to make someone else@happy by giving them flowers too."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303001,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"In other words, by giving flowers as a gift..."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"I can be close to people's hearts@and bring them kindness..."},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"That's what I wanted to do."},{"chara":[{"id":303001,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"This is something I can do@even if Blossom disappears."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"Neither my happiness nor what I want@to do will ever disappear!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303001,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"That said, before I could think like this,"},{"chara":[{"id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"I had a lot of trouble, but..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"I'm going to continue to bring@kindness to everyone with flowers."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303001}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"Hehe, what I want to do really@isn't any different than before."},{"chara":[{"id":303001,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Konomi","textRight":"I'm a very lucky person, aren't I?"},{"chara":[{"id":100851,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"Va bene."},{"chara":[{"id":100851}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"The strength to never lose sight of what you want@to do is necessary to stay a Magical Girl..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100851}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"In a way, you're the strongest of all."},{"autoTurnLast":2,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
